* TreeDB state survives restart from native data directory files.
* Authenticated requests enforce repo/path/ref scope.
* Unauthorized graph/query/search results are omitted before ranking and serialization.
* Registry placement routes writes to primary and reads to allowed primary/mirror nodes.

